<L>Da bhrathair do Aodh flionn&s;gothach<NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">Here Grig, or Achy, is wanting. The bard probably regarded Grig as an u&s;urper, or no king, (&s;ee <HI>Chron. Pict.</HI>); and Achy as a minor in Grig's power.</NOTE>.</L>
