<HEAD>NUMBER III. <HI>The &s;ucce&s;&s;ion of Scoti&s;h Kings, in&s;erted in the Chronicle of Melro&s;e;</HI><NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">By the Abbot of Dundrainan: in the thirteenth century, as the writing &s;hews.</NOTE><HI>comprizing the</HI> Chronicon Elegiacum. Gale et Fulman Scriptores Angl. Oxon. 1684, tom. I. ad finem, <HI>p.</HI> 595&mdash;598.</HEAD>
