<P>ANNO 741<NOTE N="a" PLACE="foot">Altius non incipit quia Melro&s;en&s;es Annales &s;unt Continuatio Bedae.</NOTE> obiit Ewain Rex Scottorum, cui &s;ucce&s;&s;it Murezaut<NOTE N="b" PLACE="foot">Murdac.</NOTE> filius ejus.</P>
