<P N="994">994. Rex Scottorum Kined occiditur; po&s;t quem,</P>
<LG>
<L>Rex Con&s;tantinus, Culeno filius ortus,</L>
<L>Ad caput amnis Aven en&s;e peremptus erat,</L>
